cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

Reasoning: 
1) cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with learning sentence embeddings and natural language processing. 
2) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper compares different methods of learning embeddings and evaluates their performance. 
3) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with learning representations of phrases and sentences, which is a key area of research in AI. 
4) cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper uses neural networks to learn embeddings. 
5) cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly deal with visual data, but it does use recursive networks which are commonly used in computer vision tasks.
